modules.description: This module provides functions for asynchronous serialization and writing of data using the Faraday buffer model. It supports operations like `serialize`, which writes data to a Faraday buffer and flushes it using a provided yield function, and `writev_of_fd`, which writes a list of bigstring iovecs to a file descriptor. It is used for efficient, high-performance network and file I/O in asynchronous applications.
